languages.text: "В итоге ты совершил то, в чем напрасно винил себя — предал Амарната".
"In the end, you did the thing you had needlessly accused yourself of doing. You betrayed Amarnat."
languages.original_text: "В итоге ты совершил то, в чем напрасно винил себя — предал Амарната".

languages.text: “你曾无端自我指责，但到了最后，你还是做了那样的事情。你背叛了阿玛纳特。”
languages.original_text: "In the end, you did the thing you had needlessly accused yourself of doing. You betrayed Amarnat."

languages.text: «Al final, hizo lo mismo de lo que se había acusado. Traicionó a Amarnat».

traits.locale_text: «Al final, hizo lo mismo de lo que se había acusado. Traicionó a Amarnat».

languages.text: 「結局、お前は自分自身で不必要なまでに非難していたことを成したのだ。お前はアマルナトを裏切った」
languages.original_text: "In the end, you did the thing you had needlessly accused yourself of doing. You betrayed Amarnat."

traits.locale_text: 「結局、お前は自分自身で不必要なまでに非難していたことを成したのだ。お前はアマルナトを裏切った」

languages.text: "Letztlich habt Ihr das getan, was Ihr Euch unnötigerweise selbst vorgeworfen hattet. Ihr habt Amarnat verraten."
languages.original_text: "In the end, you did the thing you had needlessly accused yourself of doing. You betrayed Amarnat."

traits.locale_text: "Letztlich habt Ihr das getan, was Ihr Euch unnötigerweise selbst vorgeworfen hattet. Ihr habt Amarnat verraten."

languages.text: « Au bout du compte, vous avez fait ce dont vous vous étiez inutilement accusé. Vous avez trahi Amarnat. »

languages.text: "Gereksiz yere kendini suçladığın şeyi yapmış oldun... Amarnat'a ihanet ettin."
languages.original_text: "In the end, you did the thing you had needlessly accused yourself of doing. You betrayed Amarnat."

traits.locale_text: "Nihayetinde yapabilecek olmakla gereksiz yere suçlandığın şeyi yaptın. Amarnat'a ihanet ettin."
